<hr class="my-5">
<h2>10. placekitten.com</h2>
<p>placekitten.com is a simple service that can be used to fetched pictures of kittens that can be used as placeholder images.</p>
<p><strong>Website</strong>: <a href="https://placekitten.com">https://placekitten.com</a></p>
<p><strong>Example HTML and image</strong>:</p>
<div class="code-block">
    <pre>
        <code data-theme="moonlight" data-lang="html" class="torchlight" style="background-color: #212539; --theme-selection-background: #aab3e5;"><!-- Syntax highlighted by torchlight.dev --><div class='line'><span style="color:#5b6395; text-align: right; -webkit-user-select: none; user-select: none;" class="line-number">1</span><span style="color: #7FDAFF;">&lt;</span><span style="color: #FF757F;">img</span><span style="color: #7FDAFF;"> </span><span style="color: #FFBD76;">src</span><span style="color: #7FDAFF;">=</span><span style="color: #7FDAFF;">&quot;</span><span style="color: #7AF8CA;">http://placekitten.com/250/250</span><span style="color: #7FDAFF;">&quot;</span><span style="color: #7FDAFF;">&gt;</span></div></code>    </pre>
</div>
